PrecisAmendment to the ACCOUNTING FOR IMPORTED GOODS AND PAYMENT OF DUTIES REGULATIONS modifying the definition of "billing period" in section 2 of the Regulations to make it clear that it applies to situations where the importer has accounted for goods as well as those where the importer was to account for goods but failed to do so.
